{"tid":1583393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十點鳩叫少人嗌 我趁呢段時間做左樣野","createTime":"2019-09-20T14:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T14:45:30.000Z","uid":216008,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"87c03dd718427b29c127923ec6cbeb05ac56149f","tid":1583393,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔知咩事 十點鳩叫少左好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔緊要 今日一無人回我<br />\n我開始發言 雖然把聲沙撚曬 但我覺得喺呢段冷清既過渡期都係一種好既文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我總共講左三次野<br />\n第一次 係講831太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二次 係聽日921唔好出沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一次 係美國法案結果如何 都唔可以停止抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發言前後我都嗌兩三次口號 直到無人帶頭/和應 我就開始講野<br />\n我覺得十點鳩叫少左人嗌 係因為大家對抗爭變得習慣<br />\n但願大家用你雄壯既聲線 好好同街坊文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後1030結束 大家不妨可以同街坊講聲「今日咁少人，但我聽日十點都會照嗌，希望大家響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n香港人 唔該真係加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf03e2850f4c0b0aecff181f4cadabb9feb9f7bd","tid":1583393,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180bdd365193ef9ec633472ba1d4721dde39e95e","tid":1583393,"uid":216008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"士氣士氣！"},{"pid":"ecfa485354683189d68261e3018d7d03f56fc069","tid":1583393,"uid":216008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"嗌呀！！！！1"},{"pid":"e2c15317baf01d2f5da53aafd2976c59b349c007","tid":1583393,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"頭先我開行個藍牙喇叭播肥媽首死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9cd8eeacdfec78cd1ba957d64f79b78ff73f57","tid":1583393,"uid":322637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46af802b4904fe9a6e960b8ea3fa0bda01b707be","tid":1583393,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG17ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=ed899b2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"ac9d6571d16a2c428535a7429856f85f224a92bd","tid":1583393,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2c15317baf01d2f5da53aafd2976c59b349c007","tid":1583393,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"頭先我開行個藍牙喇叭播肥媽首死黑警<img src=\"/asset